      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total dream. This car has been pampered since day one\u2014always garaged and kept spotless. It still has that brand-new feel and drives like it just rolled off the lot! If you're looking for something that's been loved and looks absolutely flawless, you\u2019ve found it. I\u2019m so excited for the next owner to enjoy this beauty as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
