    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the iconic S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six with individual throttle bodies. This example exhibits flawless VANOS timing and has undergone a comprehensive subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp engagement, paired with a factory-spec variable M differential lock for optimal power delivery. The suspension retains its original geometry with refreshed bushings and dampers, maintaining the precise turn-in and neutral handling characteristics this chassis is renowned for. Meticulously maintained with a documented service history, this vehicle represents a turnkey opportunity for the discerning collector.",
