      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute showroom-quality masterpiece that satisfies even the most meticulous inspection. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, resulting in an exterior finish that is entirely free of stone chips, swirls, or imperfections. The paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, further protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather upholstery remains taut and supple with no bolster wear, and the 'new car' scent persists. Every electronic feature, from the advanced infotainment system to the smallest ambient light, operates flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, backed by a comprehensive, documented service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. This sale includes all original keys, factory manuals, and a bespoke indoor car cover. For the buyer seeking a turn-key example that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line, this is the definitive choice.",
