    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2011 Porsche 911 Carrera S (997.2) in concours-ready condition. This example features the sought-after 3.8L DFI flat-six engine, producing 385 hp and 310 lb-ft of torque, mated to a precise 6-speed manual transmission. The mechanical integrity is superlative, with a clean DME report showing zero ignitions in ranges 3\u20136. Performance is enhanced by the factory-spec PASM (Porsche Active Suspension Management) and a mechanical limited-slip differential. The chassis remains taut, benefitting from original bushings and a fastidious maintenance regimen. Braking is handled by four-piston aluminum monobloc calipers over cross-drilled, internally ventilated rotors, showing minimal heat cycling. The exterior retains its factory luster with original paint throughout, while the interior leather exhibits no bolster wear or UV degradation. A rare opportunity for the discerning collector seeking peak hydraulic-steering feedback and analog engagement.",
